Goal: "When the funding goal is met, I will provide you a link to download the entire demo version of Wise 'Trip' EP (Deluxe), including the album cover artwork, as well as including CD quality .wav files of several earlier versions of \\"Destiny 'Trip'\\" and one earlier version of \\"A Brief History of Memory,\\" so you can hear how the two songs developed throughout the production process, and a cool custom electro-bass loop .wav file I produced.  The album song files will be your choice of either CD quality (44.1k 16bit) .wav files or \\"audiophile\\" quality (96k 24bit, if your equipment/software can accommodate the extremely high quality rendering; iTunes, for example, does).\\r\\n\\r\\nUpon project completion, I will provide you a link to download the finished, retail version of the album (same quality and type of files mentioned above), including the album cover artwork, AND exclusive behind-the-scenes photos of me at work producing, the equipment I use, and views of my production software sessions (all of which will not be released to the general public).  I will also personally mail you a retail version CD (w/case and cover artwork), with a PERSONALIZED autograph (according to your specifications), to an address of your choosing, using USPS First-Class Media Mail (with Signature Confirmation service for delivery within the US, or with Certificate of Mailing for international delivery).\\r\\n\\r\\nAdditionally, after project completion, I will personally call you (at a time of your choosing) and talk to you for a full hour about anything and everything you'd like to know about me, my past, my experiences in the army, my musical experiences and inspirations, my production work, my thought-provoking philosophical and physics theories, general info about my family, and my future plans.  I'll also incorporate any musical ideas, artwork, or other contribution you can make that I like towards my future productions and physically credit you by name for anything I decide to incorporate into my work.\\r\\n\\r\\nFinally, I will provide you with my personal email address so you can directly communicate with me about whatever you'd like from time to time and keep you up-to-date on what I'm currently up to, including occasionally sending you any incomplete music I'm working on at the time, to keep you intimately \\"in the loop.\\""
